::DrillBit::

Turns back to KitKat, only to see her go into stasis.
"No. Come on, come back to me."

::Hot Rod::

Hot Rod saw Prowler run up.
"Ok, lets do it!" He says, shooting plasma charges at the Predicons.

::K9::

The sounds of shots, awoke him. He ran to the exit.
"Die, Predicons!" He shoots.
